06:45.320 --> 06:47.780
Oh, my gosh, Crusaders! Pip won!

06:47.960 --> 06:50.020
I couldn't have won
without the hard work

06:50.020 --> 06:53.400
of my campaign managers,
the Cutie Mark Crusaders!

06:53.580 --> 06:55.520
Campaign Manager Cutie Marks!

06:57.920 --> 07:01.340
Guess you're not as good as
you thought, Blank Flanks!

07:01.660 --> 07:04.160
In fact, I demand a recount!

07:04.320 --> 07:06.940
Trust me, Diamond
Tiara. Pip won.

07:07.220 --> 07:09.780
I'll be the judge of
that, Miss Cheerilee!

07:11.820 --> 07:13.180
WHAAAAAAAAT??!

07:13.740 --> 07:14.460
ONE VOTE?

07:15.020 --> 07:17.840
SILVER SPOON? YOU
didn't vote for me?

07:17.920 --> 07:19.220
No, I didn't!

07:19.780 --> 07:22.080
But you're my best friend!

07:22.480 --> 07:24.840
Am I? Cause I tried
to help by mentioning

07:24.840 --> 07:26.420
your "surprise statue"

07:26.720 --> 07:29.420
and suddenly I wasn't
even allowed to speak!

07:29.760 --> 07:31.700
You could have actually
won this election

07:31.800 --> 07:34.780
if you'd just listened to
me. You wanna know how?

07:35.500 --> 07:38.020
Sorry. I'm not
allowed to speak.

07:41.480 --> 07:44.360
What? I don't have to
follow her drama anymore.

07:46.680 --> 07:49.120
I know Diamond Tiara's
been pretty awful,

07:49.120 --> 07:51.660
but we should probably
make sure she's OK.

07:52.020 --> 07:54.680
Just 'cause she's never cared
about anypony else's feelings

07:54.960 --> 07:56.780
doesn't mean we shouldn't
care about hers.

08:02.200 --> 08:05.940
Diamond Tiara, why are
you making that face?

08:06.160 --> 08:08.600
That is not the
face of a winner.

08:09.440 --> 08:12.200
Because I didn't win.

08:12.540 --> 08:16.160
What? You mean I hefted
all these party supplies

08:16.160 --> 08:17.540
to celebrate nothing?

08:19.000 --> 08:19.880
Sorry, Mother.

08:20.180 --> 08:24.380
It's bad enough you lost to that
transplant from Trottingham.

08:24.580 --> 08:28.400
But imagine if you'd lost to
one of those Blank Flanks!

08:29.060 --> 08:33.500
As a rich pony, you must always
think of your social standing!

08:35.660 --> 08:39.740
That starts here in Ponyville
and reaches all over Equestria.

08:40.060 --> 08:43.140
Don't ever forget that,
Diamond Tiara! Ever!

08:54.440 --> 08:58.660
<i> ♪ If I'm a diamond, then</i>
<i> why do I feel so rough? ♪</i>

08:59.040 --> 09:02.900
