<i>lost, I don't know what to do ♪</i>

09:51.180 --> 09:55.540
<i> ♪ The ground is sinking away,</i>
<i> I'm about to fall through ♪</i>

09:55.760 --> 09:58.320
<i> ♪ Would you believe, ♪</i>

09:58.880 --> 10:04.080
<i> ♪ that I've always wished</i>
<i> I could be somepony else ♪</i>

10:04.520 --> 10:09.600
<i> ♪ Yet I can't see,</i>
<i> what I need to do ♪</i>

10:09.600 --> 10:12.640
<i>♪ to be the pony I want to be. ♪</i>

10:18.400 --> 10:21.440
<i>♪ To be the pony I want to be ♪</i>

10:24.760 --> 10:28.040
Is it weird that I
feel bad for her?

10:28.460 --> 10:31.740
If it is, then
I'm weird too.

10:32.100 --> 10:35.060
She wants to change, but
she doesn't know how.

10:35.320 --> 10:36.980
Seems like she could
use a friend or two

10:36.980 --> 10:38.100
to help her figure it out.

10:45.280 --> 10:47.380
Hey, Diamond Tiara! Wait up!

10:48.000 --> 10:51.380
What do you three want? To
gloat? Rub in my defeat?

10:51.900 --> 10:54.700
Actually, we wanted to
invite you to our clubhouse

10:54.700 --> 10:55.440
to hang out.

10:56.460 --> 10:57.460
Really?

10:58.180 --> 10:59.250
Yeah. For real.

10:59.600 --> 11:01.400
Well, thanks to you all,

11:01.400 --> 11:04.280
I don't have any important Class
President business to attend to

11:04.280 --> 11:07.320
or anything. So,
I might as well.

11:08.380 --> 11:10.360
That sounds like a yes.

11:12.260 --> 11:16.180
So, do you three just sit around
here plotting out different ways

11:16.180 --> 11:18.060
to try and get your Cutie Marks?

11:18.500 --> 11:20.060
Actually, yeah.

11:20.960 --> 11:24.980
You three are...really lucky.

11:25.980 --> 11:26.980
We are?

11:27.220 --> 11:30.780
