12:35.780 --> 12:37.400
And help you find a solution!

12:37.860 --> 12:39.540
Thanks, Cutie Mark Crusaders!

12:40.620 --> 12:43.600
Oh, I already
have a solution.

12:43.760 --> 12:45.320
Our new Student
Pony President

12:45.320 --> 12:49.040
