office and I'll be reinstated!

12:49.440 --> 12:51.420
Where is she going?

12:51.420 --> 12:54.240
Where do you think!
C'mon, after her!

12:54.240 --> 12:55.820
Wait, I'm coming too!

12:56.240 --> 13:00.160
<i> ♪ Cutie Mark Crusaders,</i>
<i> get out of my way! ♪</i>

13:02.280 --> 13:04.240
<i> ♪ Those ponies need</i>
<i> to know the truth ♪</i>

13:04.240 --> 13:06.220
